<h2>Media queries</h2>

<p>We try to follow the "<b>Mobile first</b>" philosophy</p>
<p>NFB.ca has a 4 steps layout</p>

<code class="snipet">
<pre>
/* MOBILE FIRST */

/* TABLETTE */
@media (min-width: 704px){ }

/*ORDI*/
@media (min-width: 1100px){}

/*TV*/
@media (min-width: 1756px){}
</pre>
</code>

