<h3>Internet Explorer</h3>

<p>IE 8 doesnt understand media queries so we have to adjust layouts with a specific style sheet. Layout for IE should target a regular size computer screen, the mean that relevent styles in the @media 704px and @media 1100px queries shoud be copied or summarized in that IE specific style sheet.</p>

<code class="snipet">
<pre>
&lt;!--[if lt IE 9]&gt;
	&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; type=&quot;text/css&quot; media=&quot;all&quot; href=&quot;http://www.nfb.ca/medias/nfb_tube_static/styles/c/board-ie-fix.css&quot; /&gt;
&lt;![endif]--&gt;
</pre>
</code>



